highlights.text: Post Malone has the most spots on Top Songs Global. “Circles” is the highest at #5.
“Shape of You” by Ed Sheeran has been on Top Songs Global the longest, at 147 weeks straight.
“Que Tire Pa Lante” by Daddy Yankee is the biggest gainer on Top Songs Global, up 46 spots at #65.
“Follow God” by Kanye West is the highest new entry on Top Songs Global at #4.
